gg-@-2000x1270-amie-Squire_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/snoop-dogg-@-2000x1270-amie-Squire_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/snoop-dogg-@-2000x1270-amie-Squire_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/snoop-dogg-@-2000x1270-amie-Squire_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/snoop-dogg-@-2000x1270-amie-Squire_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/snoop-dogg-@-2000x1270-amie-Squire_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/snoop-dogg">史努比狗狗</a>在巴黎解说 2024 年夏季奥运会时即兴表演了一段关于盛装舞步的即兴自由泳。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/mount-westmore-snoop-cube-40-short-review-snoop-dogg-ice-cube-e40-too-short-g-funk-3364110">Mount Westmore –“Snoop，Cube，40，$hort”评论：说唱超级团体充满了想法和个性</a></strong></li></ul><p>今年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-snoop-dogg-carry-the-olympic-torch-through-paris-3778450">这位嘻哈传奇人物担任美国电视网<em>NBC</em>的奥运记者</a>。在凡尔赛宫频道的转播室里，他和奥运主播迈克·蒂里科 (Mike Tirico) 一起观看了一段视频，视频中一匹名叫马克西玛·贝拉 (Maxima Bella) 的马在他 1994 年的热门歌曲《杜松子酒与果汁》(Gin &amp; Juice) 中表演盛装舞步。</p><p>当斯努普看到波兰骑手桑德拉·西索耶娃（Sandra Sysojeva）的表现时，按捺不住激动的心情：“好吧，我们家有一匹LBC马，对吧？”当他意识到发生了什么事时。然后，他随着带有马术风格的标志性节奏说唱。</p><p> “<em>从前到后/有这么多的戏剧和派对，作为一匹马很难，”</em>当他的朋友斯图尔特评论马的形状和技能时，史努比说唱道。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C-SZfqqogNj/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0;