 2024 年巴黎奥运会：据报道凤凰城航空和 Air 将在闭幕式上表演https://www.nme.com/news/music/paris-olympics-2024-phoenix-and-air-to-reportedly-perform-at-fitting-ceremony-3781444?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=paris-olympics-据报道，2024 年凤凰城航空将在闭幕式上进行表演Liberty DunworthTue, 06 Aug 2024 15:04:26 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsDanceElectronic https://www.nme.com/?p=3781444 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Air-Phoenix@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Phoenix 的 Thomas Mars 和 Air 的 Nicolas Godin" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Air-Phoenix@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Air-Phoenix@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Air-Phoenix@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Air-Phoenix@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Air-Phoenix@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Air-Phoenix@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>汤姆·克鲁斯预计也将参加一个八分钟的镜头，展示他参加各种特技表演</p><p>《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paris-olympics-2024-phoenix-and-air-to-reportedly-perform-at-closing-ceremony-3781444">2024 年巴黎奥运会后：据报道 Phoenix 和 Air 将在闭幕式上表演》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Air-Phoenix@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Phoenix 的 Thomas Mars 和 Air 的 Nicolas Godin" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Air-Phoenix@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Air-Phoenix@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Air-Phoenix@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Air-Phoenix@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Air-Phoenix@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Air-Phoenix@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 7 月 26 日举行众星云集的开幕式后，人们开始猜测 2024 年巴黎奥运会闭幕式将如何举行。</p><p>活动<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/viewers-react-to-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-one-of-the-most-memorable-moments-of-2024-or-freakshow-3778508">以塞纳河沿岸史诗般的开幕式拉开序幕</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lady-gaga">Lady Gaga</a>表演法国歌舞歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-lady-gaga-perform-mon-truc-en-plumes-at-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-3778447">《Mon truc enplumes》</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gojira">Gojira</a>表演<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-gojira-perform-ah-ca-ira-in-the-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-3778455">法国大革命歌曲《Ah Ça Ira!》</a>与歌剧歌手玛丽娜·维奥蒂。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/celine-dion">席琳·迪翁 (Celine Dion)</a>也是四年来首次演出，自<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/celine-dion-reveals-stiff-person-syndrome-diagnosis-reschedules-and-cancels-shows-3363354">2022 年透露自己被诊断出患有僵人综合症 (SPS) 以来，她在首场演出中演绎了伊迪丝·琵雅芙 (Edith Piaf) 的《L&#39;Hymne A L&#39;Amour》。</a></p><p>现在，随着 2024 年分期节目的顺利进行，并将于本周日（8 月 11 日）结束，有关闭幕式的传言已经出现，凤凰城和 Air 的表演也将成为可能。</p><p>法国新闻媒体<a href="https://www.leparisien.fr/jo-paris-2024/jo-paris-2024-tom-cruise-phoenix-et-air-seront-presents-a-la-ceremonie-de-cloture-05-08-2024-H7Q54VWNONHSZEFAEBVYRSIEM4.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《巴黎人报》</em></a>首先分享了这些报道，该媒体报道说，导演托马斯·乔利（也是开幕表演的幕后黑手）正在准备另一场精彩的活动来结束奥运会两周。 </p><figure id="attachment_3781452" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3781452" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3781452" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Paris-olympics@2000x1270.jpg" alt="2024 年巴黎奥运会将于 7 月 26 日开幕" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Paris-olympics@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Paris-olympics@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Paris-olympics@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Paris-olympics@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Paris-olympics@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Paris-olympics@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3781452" class="wp-caption-text"> 2024 年巴黎奥运会将于 7 月 26 日开幕 图片来源：François-Xavier Marit-Pool/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>闭幕式的标题为“记录”，其时间将比塞纳河沿岸的闭幕式要短。时长两个小时，也将在法兰西体育场举行，描绘一个“奥运会已经消失的未来世界”。</p><p>除了众多令人期待的惊喜之外，该媒体还声称，由尼古拉斯·戈丁 (Nicholas Godin) 和让-伯努瓦·邓克尔 (Jean-Benoît Dunckel) 组成的法国电子二人组<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/air">Air</a>将在当晚进行现场表演。如果消息属实，该专辑将在乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/air-announce-moon-safari-25th-anniversary-us-dates-3598159">庆祝 1998 年首张专辑《Moon Safari》发行 25 周年之</a>际推出。</p><p>据传，凡尔赛四重奏乐团<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/phoenix">Phoenix</a>也将在当晚登上舞台，此前他们凭借 2009 年获得格莱美奖的第四张专辑“Wolfgang Amadeus Phoenix”而在全球大受欢迎。</p><p>如果两人确实在周日进行现场表演，那么他们最近将合作于 7 月 17 日在鲁瓦西机场 1 号航站楼的屋顶举办<a href="https://www.leparisien.fr/culture-loisirs/musique/concerts-de-phoenix-et-air-a-roissy-le-soir-ou-le-terminal-1-sest-transforme-en-club-a-ciel-ouvert-18-07-2024-UPDPQMXGTRA47BJA5G5OVE23HQ.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">联合音乐会</a>。</p><p>除了这两支乐队之外，好莱坞偶像<a href="/artists/tom-cruise">汤姆·克鲁斯</a>预计也将出席闭幕式——据称此举象征着从 2024 年巴黎奥运会到 2028 年洛杉矶奥运会的交接。 </p><figure id="attachment_3757052" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3757052" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3757052" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Air-Band-2024.jpg" alt="空气（摄影：Gerald Matzka/图片联盟来自 Getty Images）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Air-Band-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Air-Band-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Air-Band-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Air-Band-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Air-Band-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Air-Band-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3757052" class="wp-caption-text">航空图片来源：Gerald Matzka/图片联盟来自 Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>据该媒体报道，这位<em>《壮志凌云》</em>明星将参加由美国团队制作的长达八分钟的特技表演。据报道，其中将包括演员四月份在香榭丽舍大街附近拍摄的一场追逐的片段。</p><p>自比赛开始以来， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-celebrates-gymnast-simone-biles-historic-olympic-win-brilliance-it-doesnt-come-easy-3780502">碧昂丝</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-praises-team-usa-in-olympics-promo-video-never-be-afraid-to-show-them-who-you-are-3780901">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>在参加宣传视频后都成为头条新闻，表达了他们对美国队的支持， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/snoop-dogg-spotted-at-paris-olympics-dressage-despite-being-scared-of-horses-3780740">史努比狗狗在盛装舞步比赛中的帅气亮相吸引了人们的注意</a>——尽管他害怕马——而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/flavor-flav-goes-viral-as-official-hype-man-for-usa-water-polo-team-at-paris-olympics-3779880">风味弗拉夫作为美国水球队的官方“炒作人”而走红</a>。</p><p>另据报道，尽管<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/why-celine-dion-performed-at-the-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-for-free-3779598">席琳·迪翁谎称自己的收入为 200 万美元（150 万英镑），但她并没有收到开幕式表演的任何报酬</a>，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-what-performing-at-the-2024-paris-olympics-did-for-gojiras-streaming-numbers-3781048">哥吉拉也看到了观看演出的听众数量猛增</a>。</p><p> 《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paris-olympics-2024-phoenix-and-air-to-reportedly-perform-at-closing-ceremony-3781444">2024 年巴黎奥运会后：据报道 Phoenix 和 Air 将在闭幕式上表演》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</